<task id="task-741" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Advanced search</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">The <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-advanced-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> function allows you to find the desired test artifacts based on certain criteria. From Katalon Studio version 8.2.5, the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-advanced-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> button is located on the top right of the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-tests-explorer" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> area, next to the search bar.<p class="- topic/p "><image width="500" href="Images/KS-SEARCH-Advanced-search-button.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Advanced search button</alt></image></p><p class="- topic/p ">You can also access this function in&#160;<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Action</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-advanced-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image width="250" href="Images/KS-SEARCH-Access-advanced-search-function.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Access advanced search from main menu</alt></image></p></context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To use the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-advanced-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;function, click on the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-advanced-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;button. The&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;dialog appears. Input your search criteria, then click&#160;<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "><uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/></b>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">Katalon will query out all the matching test artifacts in the&#160;<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Search</b>&#160;tab as shown in the following picture:<p class="- topic/p "><image href="Images/KS-SEARCH-Search-results.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Advanced search results</alt></image></p></info></step></steps></taskbody></task>